name: CHEW
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
Chew is an decentralized finance (DeFi) platform built on the Shibarium that aims to provide users with a seamless and efficient DeFi experience on Shibarium. The platform offers a range of DeFi services, including yield farming, staking, lending, borrowing, and trading, all in one place. Chew’s native token is $CHEW, which is used for governance and to access various features on the platform.

Chewpad built on Shibarium that enables early-stage Shibarium projects to raise funds and launch their projects in a decentralized manner. The platform aims to provide users with access to high-quality and vetted projects that have the potential to create significant value in the Shibarium industry.

Chewswap built on the Shibarium aims to provide users with a fast and efficient trading experience. The platform allows users to trade Shibarium-based cryptocurrencies, as well as provide liquidity to earn rewards through yield farming. Chewswap’s native token is $CHEW, which is used for governance and to access various features on the platform.
